'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #3114] on 15 December 2000 at 7:09:42 pm'!"Change Set:		FlapsFix-ccnDate:			15 December 2000Author:			Chris NortonFixes a small bug in the construction of global flaps.  If the morph's world is nil, this method used to result in a walkback.  This change seems to fix it."!!Player methodsFor: 'misc' stamp: 'ccn 12/15/2000 19:03'!viewerFlapTab	"If a viewer in a flap exists for me, return it."	(costume world ifNil: [self currentWorld])		submorphsDo: [:mm |			(mm isKindOf: ViewerFlapTab)				ifTrue:					[mm scriptedPlayer == self						ifTrue: [^mm]]].	^nil! !